title: CEO of Me
description:
We are well aware it's spooky season, but Jessica and June are BRIMMING with J-O-Y and ready for a very Merry Christmas, so they're nailing down all their holiday deets ASAP. Then, the gals are leaning into thick eyeliner, red lips and strip lashes and it’s all about celebrating ourselves, baby! Deep Divers, we do NOT recommend putting on fake lashes at a stop light.
